platformAttributes.ios.subtitle.k: A story about love and life
一個關於愛與生活的故事

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: 恋心をゲームで巧みに表現
Game 7. An intimate and emotional love story.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: There is a subtle beauty to Florence. This poignant love story intertwines a succinct narrative with smart interaction design to create moments of surprising emotional weight. Conversations are turned into puzzles that evolve as the characters’ moods shift. Memories fade into focus like old Polaroid photos. The way you touch the screen becomes just as important as the plot, which makes for a story you want to steer as well as follow. Florence fosters a rare sense of intimacy with its characters, creating an impression that lingers long after the story ends.
